Alex. Brown Inc said it has declared athree-for-two stock split, payable May 29, record May 22.    The company also said it has filed to offer 912,000 commonshares, including 162,000 to be sold by a shareholder, withcompany proceeds to be used for working capital and generalcorporate purposes.  Its Alex. Brown and Sons Inc subsidiary islead underwriter.    The offering is expected to be made before the record dateof the split, the company said. Reuter&#3;